          "merged_at": null
        },
        "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nFixes #619.\r\n\r\nThis PR corrects an off-by-one behavior in the notation-highlighter transformer\r\n(`@shikijs/transformers`) where `// [!code highlight:N]` unintentionally\r\nincluded the comment's own line in the computed highlight range.\r\n\r\n**Change made**\r\n- Shift the computed range so that highlighting begins on the line *after*\r\n  the notation comment:\r\n  ```ts\r\n  // before\r\n  start = lineNumber\r\n  end   = lineNumber + count\r\n\r\n  // after\r\n  start = lineNumber + 1\r\n  end   = lineNumber + 1 + count\r\n",
        "reactions": {
